      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Skill: KnowledgeResearchIntegrity\n\n**Category:** Validation / Nodeset Integrity\n\n**Intent:** Validate Knowledge / Research graphs against the current v1 contract, report provenance and synthesis drift, and only propose bounded metadata repairs.\n\nThis graph is the contract.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
