    {
      "id": "knowledge-research-skill-contract-scope",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Scope",
      "position": {
        "x": -980,
        "y": 380
      },
      "width": 760,
      "height": 360,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Scope\n\nThis skill:\n- validates v1 node membership\n- validates provenance fields for `evidence` and `source`\n- validates `claim` evidence refs\n- validates `summary` backing refs\n- reports broken summary or contract surfaces\n\nThis skill does NOT:\n- invent missing evidence\n- rewrite claim statements\n- rewrite source meaning\n- auto-promote deferred types",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
