    {
      "id": "knowledge-research-skill-contract-failures",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Failure Modes",
      "position": {
        "x": -120,
        "y": 820
      },
      "width": 760,
      "height": 360,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Failure Modes\n\n- unknown authoritative node type: drift error\n- missing provenance on `evidence`: blocking error\n- missing durable identity on `source`: blocking error\n- missing `claim` evidence refs: warning or error depending on policy\n- missing `summary` backing refs: warning or error depending on policy\n- broken summary surface wiring: blocking error",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
