    {
      "id": "knowledge-research-skill-contract-ai",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Notes For AI",
      "position": {
        "x": 740,
        "y": 820
      },
      "width": 880,
      "height": 340,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Notes For AI\n\n- Fail on provenance gaps.\n- Never auto-rewrite claim or evidence text.\n- Restrict repair to metadata, labels, references, and report surfaces.\n- Treat deferred types as visible pressure, not valid v1 substitutions.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
